--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
README : Breakpointer
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Breakpointer is a novel tool for locating SV breakpoints from the alignment of 
single end reads. You can redistribute it and/or modify it under the terms of 
the GNU General Public License.

I.   Learn More

II.  Installation

III. Usage

IV.  Contact

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
I. Learn More:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Breakpointer is implemented in C++ and perl. 

